thread.title: Lisa & Daniel
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Lisa & Daniel

author: Lisa & Daniel
title: Lisa & Daniel
text:
I first met Michelle Portelli a couple of years ago in relation to a different property. She made a very good impression and maintained contact in such a professional way that the decision to employ her and Nelson Alexander to sell our property was an easy one. Michelles knowledge of the local property market is exemplary and her guidance and advice helped us to achieve a fantastic result come auction day.
I have no hesitation in recommending Michelle to others looking for a knowledgable, friendly and professional agent.
